==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: -ive
<hw>-ive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr> <pos>suff.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>-ivus</ets>.]</ety> <def>An adjective suffix signifying
<sig>relating</sig> or <sig>belonging to</sig>, <sig>of the nature
of</sig>, <sig>tending to</sig>; <as>as, affirmat<ex>ive</ex>,
act<ex>ive</ex>, conclus<ex>ive</ex>, correct<ex>ive</ex>,
diminut<ex>ive</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ivied</ent>⟦br⟧
